=== Cultural properties ===
=== Important Cultural Property ===
* Main hall
A three-bay {{ill|lt=kirizuma-zukuri|Q13308575|WD=Q13308575|1=Kirizuma-style}} structure with cypress bark roof, built in the {{ill|lt=Azuchi-Momoyama period|Q319531|WD=Q319531|lt=Momoyama period|1=Azuchi–Momoyama period}}. National Important Cultural Property.<ref>[http://www.city.tenri.nara.jp/kurashi/kyouiku/bunkazai/1391410354160.html Wanishita Shrine (Tenri City site)]</ref>

